{"tid":1153293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港麻疹終於都要社區爆發？","createTime":"2019-05-13T13:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T17:00:48.000Z","uid":213877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"255952185fb2b362bd6bdd45950e4a46e05ad563","tid":1153293,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457341-20190513.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457341-20190513.htm&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=54a6bbe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457341-20190513.htm&h=1764f790\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457341-20190513.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀海港城店舖GUCCI有三名銷售員，確診感染麻疹，三人情況穩定，於可傳染期內並無到其他分店工作，潛伏期內亦無接觸麻疹病人，他們的家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵，正接受醫學監察。<br />\n<br />\n三宗個案分別涉及一男兩女，過往健康良好，報稱曾接種麻疹疫苗，近日先後發燒及出疹。<br />\n<br />\n其中30歲男子在上星期二至六、即病毒傳染期，到過日本東京，曾乘坐航班UO848及UO33。<br />\n<br />\n另外兩名25歲女子，上星期都有在店內工作；一人於病毒傳染期內曾前往深圳，另一就於潛伏期內曾到過澳門。<br />\n<br />\n他們分別到過廣華、將軍澳醫院急症室求診，其後分別入住瑪嘉烈、屯門及將軍澳醫院。<br />\n<br />\n有關店舖有195名員工，衞生防護中心已為當中96人補種麻疹疫苗，明日會繼續補種疫苗。"},{"pid":"3e85a891082aed09bef369b7d34405664aa4f433","tid":1153293,"uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"一爆開就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人口密度又高<br />\n好野"},{"pid":"4a1cc6c913edc0fdf418f2f96b8ee2e7ad4b1564","tid":1153293,"uid":39181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"打左針都有麻疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e12f9d0f48d88fbf7bd9559f3697b982e3528f2","tid":1153293,"uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a1cc6c913edc0fdf418f2f96b8ee2e7ad4b1564","tid":1153293,"uid":39181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"打左針都有麻疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你呢種思想真是唔要得"},{"pid":"204eb5318bbd5c99f516e3afebbd492ebe28b1c6","tid":1153293,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"上車機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7db62a0cda9275b6c5b77bc292ae6f59bfea19","tid":1153293,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"又送禮 屌你老味＿"},{"pid":"c29ac8ed0e1345b88f360d31eab6681df1d986d8","tid":1153293,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家儲定錢, 下個業主好快到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286c2f02db847ea9e8ba1b3ae094e82213918fa9","tid":1153293,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"淘大爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61ed2245407859f18ae779ad2262facc6586a46","tid":1153293,"uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"又大送ver 2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecae43b23fa5d01bb0678bf2b0f1a980345dd95","tid":1153293,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"正常打左針 身體嘅白血球會認得隻菌/病毒"}]}